<p> <note type="source" target="#right(301)">Ysv<hi rend="sup">PT</hi>: candrārkau netrayormadhye jaṅghā lomasu sākṣiṇaḥ | tṛṇagulmādikañcāpi viśvarūpaṃ smaret tataḥ |</note><anchor xml:id="301"/><note type="source" target="#right(302)">SSP 3.13: candrasūryau netradvaye vasataḥ | anekavṛkṣalaṭāgulmatṛṇāni jaṅghāromakakūpasthāne vasanti |</note><anchor xml:id="302"/>candra<app><lem wit="#ceteri">sūryau</lem><rdg wit="#B #D #L">°sūryo</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#D #E #P">dvayor ne</lem><rdg wit="#B">dvayā°</rdg><rdg wit="#L #U2">dvayo</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">om.</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#D #E">trayor ma</lem><rdg wit="#P">netreyor</rdg><rdg wit="#B">netrayo</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">netrayoḥ</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">netradvaya</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">dhye</lem><rdg wit="#U1">om.</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">vartate</lem><rdg wit="#U2">pravartate</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">vasaṃti</rdg></app>/ <app><lem wit="#B #E #L #P">anekavanaspatigulmalatātṛṇāni</lem><rdg wit="#D">anaikavanaspatigulmatṛṇāni</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">anekavanaspatīgulmalatāni</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">anekavana | spatigulmalatātṛṇāni</rdg></app> jaṅghā<app><lem wit="#ceteri">roma</lem><rdg wit="#B #L">°rora°</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#ceteri">madhye</lem><rdg wit="#D">sthāne</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">vasanti</lem><rdg wit="#U2">vasati</rdg><rdg wit="#D">varttaṃte</rdg></app>/ <note type="source" target="#right(303)">Ysv<hi rend="sup">PT</hi>: samagradarśanān muktaḥ svargabhogañ ca matsukham | tad etac cintayā yāti rogaśokavivarjjitaḥ |</note><anchor xml:id="303"/><note type="source" target="#right(304)">SSP 3.14: yat sukhaṃ tat svargaṃ yad duḥkhaṃ tan narakaṃ yat karma tad bandhanaṃ yan nirvikalpaṃ tan muktiḥ svasvarūpadaśāyāṃ nidrādau svātmajāgaraḥ śāntir bhavati | evaṃ sarvadeheṣu viśvasvarūpaḥ parameśvaraḥ paramātmā akhaṇḍasvabhāvena ghaṭe ghaṭe citsvarūpī tiṣṭhati ||3.14||</note><anchor xml:id="304"/><app><lem wit="#ceteri">puruṣasya</lem><rdg wit="#U1">puruṣasyāvādya</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#D #E #P">nṛtyadarśanāt</lem><rdg wit="#D">nityadarśanād</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">darśanāt ||</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">nṛtyod°</rdg></app>// <app><lem wit="#ceteri">gītaśravaṇāt</lem><rdg wit="#U1">gītaśravaṇād</rdg></app>// vallabhavastuno <app><lem wit="#U1">darśanāt</lem><rdg wit="#U1">darśanād</rdg></app>// <app><lem wit="#P">ya</lem><rdg wit="#U1">yā</rdg><rdg wit="#B #D #E #L">yaḥ</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">om.</rdg></app> ānanda utpadyate <app><lem wit="#E">saḥ</lem><rdg wit="#D #U1 #U2">sa</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#B #E #L #P">svargalokaḥ</lem><rdg wit="#U2">svargaloka</rdg><rdg wit="#D">bahurānaṃdaḥ svargaphulaḥ</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">bahurānaṃdaḥ svargaphalaḥ</rdg></app> kathyate/ roga<app><lem wit="#E">pīḍito</lem><rdg wit="#P #B">°pīḍato</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">°pīḍāto</rdg><rdg wit="#L">°pīḍano</rdg><rdg wit="#D">°pīḍā</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">°pīḍa</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">durjanebhyaḥ</lem><rdg wit="#P #B #L">durjanebhya</rdg></app> puruṣasya <app><lem wit="#L">yad duḥkhaṃ</lem><rdg wit="#E">yat duḥkham</rdg><rdg wit="#B">yat duḥkha</rdg><rdg wit="#P">yaduḥkham</rdg><rdg wit="#D #U1">duḥkhaṃ</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">duḥkha</rdg></app> utpadyate/ <app><lem wit="#ceteri">tad bahutaraṃ</lem><rdg wit="#D">tat bahutaraṃ</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">bahutaraṃ</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">narakaṃ</lem><rdg wit="#U1">nakaṃ</rdg></app> kathyate/ atha ca yatkarmakaraṇāt sarveṣāṃ lokānāṃ svamanasī ca śubhaṃ na bharate tatkarma baṃdhanam ity ucyate/ <note type="source" target="#right(305)">Ysv<hi rend="sup">PT</hi>: tad etac cintayā yāti rogaśokavivarjjitaḥ | yatkarmā karmaṇā śaṅkā manomadhye bhavedvahiḥ | tatkarmakaraṇaṃ muktir ity āha bhagavān śivaḥ |</note><anchor xml:id="305"/><note type="philcomm" target="#right(306)">This sentence is only preserved in witness U<hi rend="sub">1</hi>.</note><anchor xml:id="306"/>atha ca <app><lem wit="#P #U2">yatkarmakaraṇān ma</lem><rdg wit="#ceteri">yatkarmakaraṇāt</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#ceteri">nomadhye</lem><rdg wit="#B #L">manobudhye</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">śaṅkā</lem><rdg wit="#U2">śakā</rdg></app> na <app><lem wit="#ceteri">bhavati</lem><rdg wit="#U2">bhavaṃti</rdg></app> tatkarma <app><lem wit="#ceteri">muktikāraṇaṃ</lem><rdg wit="#L #B">kamuktikāraṇam</rdg></app>/ <app><lem wit="#ceteri">idānīṃ</lem><rdg wit="#B #P #U2">idānī</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#D #E #L">rājayogāc charīre</lem><rdg wit="#B">rājayogāc charīre ||</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">rājayogācharīre</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">rājayogāśarīre</rdg><rdg wit="#P">rogayogācharīre</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">etādṛśāni</lem><rdg wit="#E">yādṛśāni</rdg></app> cihnāni bhavanti/ tāni kathyante/ <app><lem wit="#ceteri">sakalaroganāśaḥ</lem><rdg wit="#U1">sakalarogaḥ nāśaḥ</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">sakalapṛthvīṃ</lem><rdg wit="#P">sakalāṃ pṛthvīṃ</rdg></app> paśyati/ <app><lem wit="#ceteri">tad anantaraṃ</lem><rdg wit="#P">tad aṃtaraṃ</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">tad anaṃtara°</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#D #U1">tattvaviṣayaṃ</lem><rdg wit="#ceteri">om.</rdg></app> jñānam utpadyate/ <app><lem wit="#P #D #U1">samagrāṃ bhāṣāṃ</lem><rdg wit="#E #U2">samagrā bhāṣā</rdg><rdg wit="#B">samagrā bhāṣa</rdg><rdg wit="#L">samagra bhāṣā</rdg></app> jānāti/ tataḥ puruṣasya deho vajramayo bhavati sarpa<app><lem wit="#E">daṃśena</lem><rdg wit="#P">°daṃśo</rdg><rdg wit="#B">°daṃśema</rdg><rdg wit="#ceteri">°daṃśe</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#D #U1">satī</lem><rdg wit="#ceteri">om.</rdg></app> maraṇaṃ <app><lem wit="#ceteri">na</lem><rdg wit="#L">om.</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">bhavati</lem><rdg wit="#B">bhavatī</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">vati</rdg></app>/ <app><lem wit="#ceteri">tataḥ</lem><rdg wit="#B #L">tat°</rdg></app> <note type="philcomm" target="#right(307)">The sentence is om.in U<hi rend="sub">1</hi>.</note><anchor xml:id="307"/>puruṣasya <app><lem wit="#E #D #U2">bubhukṣā</lem><rdg wit="#P">bunnukṣā</rdg><rdg wit="#B #L">babhukṣā</rdg></app>pipāsa<app><lem wit="#L">nidroṣṇatā</lem><rdg wit="#U2">°nidroṣṭṇatā°</rdg><rdg wit="#D">nidrā | uṣṇatā ||</rdg><rdg wit="#E #B">nidrollatā</rdg><rdg wit="#P">nidrolmatā</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#ceteri">śīta</lem><rdg wit="#P">śītatā</rdg><rdg wit="#E">śītoṣṇatā</rdg><rdg wit="#D">śīta nā</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#P #B #L">bādhā</lem><rdg wit="#E #D #U2">bādhāṃ</rdg></app> na <app><lem wit="#ceteri">kurvanti</lem><rdg wit="#D">kuroti</rdg></app>/ </p>
